data.description: * Multiple Offers* Highest and Best Due 7/20/2021  Beautiful 4 Bedroom, 3 full bath, Plus Den/Office/Flex room in gated community with amenities. This is a Triple-split plan with 4 large bedrooms, den, 9-foot ceilings, 8-foot doors, rounded corners and upgraded fixtures. Spacious owner's suite with huge gorgeous bath featuring separate vanities. Granite & stainless kitchen has tube skylight, eat-at bar, desk, and breakfast nook. Three car garage with built-in storage. Nature & sunset views with  no rear neighbors visible from the expansive rear windows and French doors.TerraLargo features tile roofs, paver driveways, and a resort-style pool & fitness center.    Five-minutes from I-4, shops, restaurants, and mall. This home needs a little TLC but you can make it yours! Call today before it's gone!
